  <brief_title>Seroquel- Agitation Associated With Dementia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Double-Blind, Randomized, Comparison of the Efficacy and Safety of Quetiapine Fumarate (SEROQUEL) and Placebo in the Treatment of Agitation Associated With Dementia.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
